item.description:
#Travel A small stone, worked to resemble a regular geometric shape. A glowing, fluctuating coloured line runs over the entire stone, dividing it in two halves. One face has the divider widen into what resembles a keyhole, which also takes on another geometric shape. You obtained a key with it, which fits perfectly into the breach.
It seems to magnetically attract the key&hellip;
When the Key is inserted, the divider will vanish, dropping the two shells and open up a temporary rift to any bound location.
